com.github.fge.grappa.transform.hash

Class InstructionGroupHasher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
      • com.github.fge.grappa.transform.hash.InstructionGroupHasher

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class InstructionGroupHasher
extends org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
    Hashing for an InstructionGroup

    Not very pretty, that one.

    The only entry point, hash(InstructionGroup, String), will hash the entire instructions and field out of the instruction group, then set the name of the instruction group appropriately.

    See Also:
    InstructionGroupPreparer
